    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="transcript" id="F4A">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>I have a Bird in spring </l>
                    <l>Which for myself doth sing - </l>
                    <l>The spring decoys.  </l>
                    <l>And as the summer nears - </l>
                    <l>And as the Rose appears,</l>
                    <l>Robin is gone.  </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Yet do I not repine </l>
                    <l>Knowing that Bird of mine </l>
                    <l>Though flown - </l>
                    <l>Learneth beyond the sea</l>
                    <l>Melody new for me </l>
                    <l>And will return.  </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Fast in a safer hand </l>
                    <l>Held in a truer Land </l>
                    <l>Are mine -</l>
                    <l>And though they now depart, </l>
                    <l>Tell I my doubting heart </l>
                    <l>They're thine.<app type="division"><lem><pb/></lem></app>
  </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>In a serener Bright, </l>
                    <l>In a more golden light</l>
                    <l>I see </l>
                    <l>Each little doubt and fear, </l>
                    <l>Each little discord here </l>
                    <l>Removed.  </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Then will I not repine,</l>
                    <l>Knowing that Bird of mine </l>
                    <l>Though flown </l>
                    <l>Shall in a distant tree </l>
                    <l>Bright melody for me </l>
                    <l>Return.</l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
